Precision Medicine Approach to Anaplastic Thyroid Cancer: Advances in Targeted 
Drug Therapy Based on Specific Signaling Pathways.

Samimi H(1), Fallah P(2), Naderi Sohi A(3), Tavakoli R(4), Naderi M(5), 
