(1)State Geological Institute of Dionyz Stur, Mlynská Dolina 1, 817 04 
Bratislava, Slovak Republic. stanislav.rapant@geology.sk.
(2)State Geological Institute of Dionyz Stur, Mlynská Dolina 1, 817 04 
Bratislava, Slovak Republic. veronika.cveckova@geology.sk.
(3)State Geological Institute of Dionyz Stur, Mlynská Dolina 1, 817 04 
